## turn and shoot if enemy is directly to the left or right
sp {attack*propose*turn-and-fire
   (state <s> ^name attack
              ^status.enemy-sighted <es>)
   (<es> ^direction { << left right >> <dir> }
         ^position center)
   -->
   (<s> ^operator <o> + =)
   (<o> ^name turn
        ^actions <a>)
   (<a> ^rotate.direction <dir>
        ^fire.weapon missile)}
